---
title: Asian-Style Hoisin Chicken Bao Buns with Chilli Bacon Fries & Cucumber Salad
description: It’s bao-o’clock again - who could ever get enough of these little clouds of yum? This time, we’ve brought in a garlicky chicken and hoisin sauce filling, a refreshing cucumber salad and bacon chilli fries for an extra treat!
